name: lbl-repack
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "lbl-repack" %}
{% set version = "1.4.4" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/lbl-repack-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 2d9d89604c30795c89fba54a7ff423f868d1645ef3bf2ee53141220b409b4507

build:
  number: 1
  skip: true  # [win]
  skip: true  # [py<35]
  entry_points:
    - repack = repack.__main__:main
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
  host:
    - numpy
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - numpy >=1.13.3
    - python
    - scipy >=0.17.1
    - {{ pin_compatible('numpy') }}

test:
  imports:
    - repack

about:
  home: https://github.com/pcubillos/repack
  summary: A line-transition data compression package
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  dev_url: https://github.com/pcubillos/repack

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pcubillos
